&lt;p&gt;The ICQA Analyst is a floor-level inventory accuracy and compliance role responsible for executing cycle counts, investigating discrepancies, and ensuring that inventory transactions and documentation meet Factor&#39;s control standards. This is a hands-on role with direct impact on the accuracy of inventory data used across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
