&lt;li&gt;Partner with warehouse and operations teams to enforce inventory SOPs and proper handling procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and contribute data to ICQA KPI reporting (accuracy %, adjustment rate, shrinkage %)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
