&lt;p&gt;As you may have read in the news …..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“HelloFresh Acquires Ready-to-Eat Meal Company Factor75, Inc.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The acquisition marks the next step in HelloFresh’s growth plan in the US to strengthen its leading position and to expand its total addressable market&lt;/li&gt;
