&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Quality Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the North American quality reporting suite. You will evolve our real-time data capabilities to provide the business with predictive insights rather than just post-mortem reports.&lt;/li&gt;
