&lt;p&gt;Factor is a fast-scaling, fresh and healthy ready meal brand reshaping how consumers interact with food and wellness. As part of our mission to deliver healthy, convenient, and delicious meals across Europe, we’re building a world-class digital marketing team that thrives at the intersection of performance, creativity, and technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced and visionary &lt;strong&gt;Associate Director of Online Marketing&lt;/strong&gt; to lead our online acquisition efforts across paid digital channels. This role is perfect for someone who combines strong analytical acumen with a deep understanding of creative optimisation and the evolving power of AI-driven automation. You will be a key driver of scalable growth and help Factor become the most trusted nutrition brand in Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
