&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI tools and automation platforms to brief/produce content, streamline workflows, enhance targeting, and maximise ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with high-performing teams of channel managers and specialists, fostering a culture of experimentation, innovation, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with Data, CRM, Product, and Brand to align online marketing with broader customer lifecycle goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate campaign results into actionable insights and present learnings regularly to leadership stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously evaluate new channels, tools, and automation opportunities to stay ahead in the dynamic digital marketing landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
