&lt;li&gt;Deep experience with Meta Ads, Google Ads, YouTube, and programmatic platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in AI-powered marketing tools and creative automation platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic mindset with the ability to zoom in on data and zoom out to vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for data-informed storytelling and testing-led growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management and cross-functional collaboration skills.&lt;/li&gt;
