&lt;li&gt;Manage the production and fulfillment planning teams across the Factor US network, driving deliverable accountability and setting team roadmaps.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct analysis of our current Factor operations metrics and identify new key insights to optimize production planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead continuous improvement projects around planning data inputs and analysis throughout all business units.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with our internal teams to promote creative analysis of gaps in production delivery&lt;/li&gt;
